data.description: **ATTENTION BUYERS- Ask about a 5.75% rate for qualified buyers or an Assumable VA Loan at 3.25% to qualified buyers.**         Welcome home to 9015 Raven Pointe, nestled in the enchanting, highly sought after neighborhood of River Rock Ranch, situated along the picturesque Boerne Stage Road on San Antonio's North Side. This stunning home embodies the perfect blend of a quiet, outside of the city limits feel all while being located nearby The Rim and La Cantera shopping, restaurants, and entertainment.  This beautiful home boasts an elegant yet functional design, crafted with the needs of a modern owners in mind, including a private office perfect for the remote worker.  The spacious layout offers plenty of room for everyone, with four bedrooms and three bathrooms providing ample space for privacy and relaxation. The open-concept living areas provide a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining area, family room, and bonus media room, making it easy to connect and spend quality time together.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with a gas cooktop, Whirlpool appliances, sleek countertops, and abundant storage space. Whether you're preparing a gourmet meal or a quick snack, this kitchen will inspire your culinary creativity. Just off the dining area of the kitchen, the backdoor leads you to a covered patio waiting for backyard cook outs and memories under the quiet night skies.  This impeccably taken care of home with many upgraded features is waiting for its' new owners. Book your private showing today!
